data.name: Label2.Text
data.value:
-> This System has two end users. i.e. Administrator and Staff.
-> According to the type of the user authorities and rights to use the system are granted.
-> Staff users have the authority required for record maintainance in the system which helps admin to take quick decisions.
-> Here in the tree view each menu item provided to the Staff is elaborated in deep. Please procced to further nodes to solve your queries.
Thank You, Developers.

data.name: Label3.Text
data.value:
-> This is the 1st menu item for the Staff.
This function has three sub menus i.e. Add New Customer, Add New Connection and Termination of Connection
Add New : With the help of this menu the staff user can enter all the details of the new customer and store it in database for future use.
Add New Connection : This menu is useful when the existing customer wants another new connection. This saves the time to fill all details again.
Terminate : If in case some customer wants to cancel the connection, this menu is helpful.

data.name: Label5.Text
data.value:
-> This is the 2nd menu item for the Staff.
This function has 3 sub menus i.e.Transfer of Connection, Change in Billing Plan and Searching of the records.
Transfer : This menu helps staff users to change the address of the customer on their request by taking some proof and inform this to technical department for transferring the Connection to the new address.
Change Billing Plan : This menu is useful when the existing customer wants to change their billing plans according to their convienince.
Search : It helps staff users to search for the particular customer. For this some options are given like by Name, Contact No.,Customer ID, Unpaid Bills etc.

data.name: Label7.Text
data.value:
-> This is the third function for the Staff.
This function has two sub menus i.e. Bill Payment and Bill Logs
Bill Payment : This menu helps staff users to accept the bill payments from the customer and provide them receipt. It also contains an option to generate the duplicate bill on customer request as details are provided by the technical department.
Bill Logs : This menu helps the staff users to get the bill payment details of every customer by selecting different options.

data.name: Label9.Text
data.value:
-> This is the 5th function for the Staff Members.
This function is having 2 sub menus i.e. Register Complaints and Guest Entry. Customer Satisfaction is the basic motto of the service provider company.
Register Complaints : The complaints of the customers are to be recorded in this menu so its helpful for respective departments to solve the customers problem in minimum time. Guest Entry : The details of the guest who had visited the company for the inquiry related to connections, Plans etc are to be maintained using this menu.

data.name: Label11.Text
data.value:
-> This is the 4th menu item for the Staff.
This function has two menus i.e. Change Password and Log Off
Change Password : This menu helps staff members to change their own password given by the admin on entry in the company, according to his/her choice.
Log Off : With this menu the Staff is logged off from the system. Security of data in the system is assured by logging off the system and avoid unauthrized usage by others.

data.name: Label13.Text
data.value:
-> This funtion helps the Staff to know what actually this system contains and about all the functionality for the rights provided to him/her.
This contains two submenus i.e. General Tips and About us.
General Tips : This helps Staff users if he/she gets stuck at any point in the system. The tips provided to him will help him/her in completing the task. The desciption of the menus is also given in details. In simple words this menu items opens up this current form.
About Us : This menu shows the details about version of the software, manufacture date and about the developers of the system.
